=Episode 15=

3
00:02:15,730 --> 00:02:16,610
Cui Haitao,

4
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:20,100
you once joined a tomb raiding gang.

5
00:02:20,850 --> 00:02:22,580
What was your relation to Wang Bingde?

6
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:24,610
Nothing between us.

7
00:02:28,850 --> 00:02:29,730
Look,

8
00:02:30,450 --> 00:02:31,860
I've served my time

9
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:34,210
and paid my dues.

10
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:36,580
Now I'm

11
00:02:36,850 --> 00:02:37,730
clean.

12
00:02:40,730 --> 00:02:41,980
He just came to eat.

13
00:03:00,730 --> 00:03:01,610
Cui Haitao!

14
00:03:03,570 --> 00:03:05,010
Captain! Captain! Captain!

15
00:03:05,010 --> 00:03:06,130
- Captain!
- Xu Xiao.

16
00:03:06,130 --> 00:03:07,010
Don't stop me.

17
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:08,330
Xu Xiao, what are you doing?

18
00:03:09,450 --> 00:03:10,330
Come out here.

19
00:03:18,730 --> 00:03:19,620
Xu Xiao.

20
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:20,550
Xu Xiao,

21
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:21,660
stay calm.

22
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:22,650
I get how you feel.

23
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:25,020
I know, but Cui Haitao...

24
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:26,340
Don't give me the "but".

25
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:27,360
Lin Guoqiang's daughter...

26
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,700
I understand your feelings.

27
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:34,020
My bad, I was too hasty.

28
00:03:35,730 --> 00:03:37,170
I'll handle myself better.

29
00:03:38,290 --> 00:03:40,100
No worries. Can I go in now?

30
00:03:43,220 --> 00:03:45,100
Trust me, I'll get it together.

31
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:51,290
Go ahead.

32
00:03:51,820 --> 00:03:52,770
Keep your cool.

33
00:03:53,170 --> 00:03:54,050
No problem.

34
00:03:54,050 --> 00:03:57,140
(Interrogation Room)

35
00:04:25,780 --> 00:04:26,660
Start talking.

36
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:31,060
How long have you been at this?

37
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:33,130
Seven or eight years.

38
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,210
How many kids do you have?

39
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:43,780
Two.

40
00:04:45,250 --> 00:04:46,180
One's seven.

41
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:48,420
One's five.

42
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:50,780
A son and a daughter?

43
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:01,200
Does this business make money?

44
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:02,560
It's so-so.

45
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,460
In a year,

46
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,980
I make around 100,000.

47
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:08,860
So your life

48
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:10,300
is going pretty well.

49
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:12,060
Just okay.

50
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,300
Thanks to my wife

51
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:16,460
for not minding.

52
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:20,820
Have you ever thought

53
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:23,100
you'll lose it all

54
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:25,420
overnight?

55
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:28,740
Like

56
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:30,140
tomorrow?

57
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:04,700
It's not that I don't want to say.

58
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:06,420
I'm just afraid to say.

59
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:09,820
Xiang is ruthless.

60
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:11,580
These people

61
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:13,740
can do anything.

62
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:19,180
Who's Xiang?

63
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,260
Cui Haitao, listen up.

64
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:34,940
If you tell me the truth,

65
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,740
I can keep your family safe.

66
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:45,420
Why should I trust you?

67
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:46,980
Because you're here now,

68
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:48,350
you have no choice but to trust me.

69
00:06:48,350 --> 00:06:49,140
Got it?

70
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:50,420
There's no way out for you.

71
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,640
If you don't speak the truth,

72
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:54,100
you'll stay stuck here.

73
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:14,620
Xiang is

74
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:17,500
Wang Bingde.

75
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,100
His real name is

76
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:28,940
Wang Xiang.

77
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:34,940
Jiahei,

78
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,700
there's nothing here.

79
00:07:37,380 --> 00:07:38,940
It's all been cleared out, right?

80
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:41,220
Keep looking.

81
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:02,700
What are you hiding?

82
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:03,580
Nothing.

83
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:05,300
Found anything good?

84
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:07,260
Nothing.

85
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,140
What are you hiding?

86
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:10,020
Nothing at all.

87
00:08:10,020 --> 00:08:10,950
Keeping it to yourself?

88
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:11,860
Who's keeping anything?

89
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:12,980
You've got me wrong.

90
00:08:12,980 --> 00:08:13,860
Really, nothing.

91
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,140
Buddy,

92
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:17,180
you're breaking the rules.

93
00:08:17,180 --> 00:08:18,060
What rules?

94
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:20,140
We share everything, the three of us.

95
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:21,980
What rules?!

96
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,740
Everyone earns their keep here.

97
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:25,100
Finder's keepers, right?

98
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:26,180
Everyone earns their keep?

99
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,060
Exactly.

100
00:08:28,210 --> 00:08:29,440
Everyone earns their keep, huh?

101
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:32,260
- Wang Xiang.
- Don't act recklessly.

102
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:33,140
Follow the rules.

103
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,400
Help him finish me off, huh?

104
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:35,760
Soon he'll be after you too.

105
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:51,780
Good buddy.

106
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:52,980
Good buddy.

107
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:10,660
In my younger days,

108
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:13,340
I once worked with them.

109
00:09:14,420 --> 00:09:15,300
Later on,

110
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:16,780
I spent three years in jail.

111
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:19,460
After getting out,

112
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,220
I worked at Wang Bingde's site.

113
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:23,140
Eventually he

114
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:24,940
brought me into their gang.

115
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:27,020
What's your role in this gang?

116
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:28,380
Tomb blasting.

117
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:31,020
Few know this skill.

118
00:09:31,380 --> 00:09:34,060
Wang Bingde taught me himself.

119
00:09:35,740 --> 00:09:38,220
I'm just a peripheral member,

120
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,270
mainly handling technical stuff.

121
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:43,340
Does Wang Bingde handle tomb blasting too?

122
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:44,860
No,

123
00:09:44,860 --> 00:09:45,780
he's the underboss,

124
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,100
a strategist.

125
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:49,420
How long have you been doing this?

126
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:51,180
For quite a while now.

127
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:54,740
Then,

128
00:09:55,740 --> 00:09:56,700
something happened.

129
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,140
I felt like

130
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:00,420
this gang was a bit...

131
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:03,620
a bit twisted.

132
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:05,540
So I left.

133
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,220
What made you

134
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:08,660
leave the gang?

135
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:10,660
Hei...

136
00:10:12,660 --> 00:10:13,540
Zhou Jiahei

137
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,940
unearthed a wet corpse

138
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:18,420
and found many bamboo slips.

139
00:10:19,300 --> 00:10:20,540
Come on. Hurry up!

140
00:10:20,540 --> 00:10:22,060
Clear everything off the table.

141
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:23,950
- On it!
- Okay!

142
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:35,300
Uncle, this is a wet corpse.

143
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:36,660
Why did you bring it back?

144
00:10:36,860 --> 00:10:37,980
I haven't seen a non-decaying

145
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:39,300
wet corpse in years.

146
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:40,380
Quick, quick, quick.

147
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:42,300
Master,

148
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,460
can this sell for money?

149
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:46,180
Many people want it.

150
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:47,420
It's very useful.

151
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:48,900
Come.

152
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:53,980
This is...?

153
00:10:54,180 --> 00:10:55,420
What's it used for?

154
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:59,940
I've been seeking a secret.

155
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:02,660
A huge secret.

156
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:06,660
Worth more than hundreds of tombs.

157
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:16,900
Help me check this character.

158
00:11:18,020 --> 00:11:19,260
See that? This one.

159
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:26,340
Daming.

160
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:32,060
Fell asleep?

161
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,500
Get the dictionary.

162
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:44,420
This character.

163
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:49,420
Where to turn, you fool?

164
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:50,700
Isn't that the character?

165
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:55,420
On this bamboo slip,

166
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:57,660
he discovered

167
00:11:58,140 --> 00:11:59,130
the secret to immortality

168
00:12:00,180 --> 00:12:01,660
buried in a nearby tomb.

169
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:03,820
Later on,

170
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:06,660
he took us

171
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:08,540
to Yu County and excavated the tomb.

172
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:11,180
In that ancient tomb,

173
00:12:12,260 --> 00:12:13,700
it's said a monarch was buried.

174
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:16,060
The tomb had water seepage,

175
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:17,380
making it unsafe.

176
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,100
The tomb passage

177
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:20,100
was flooded,

178
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:22,380
which prevented further looting

179
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:23,760
and protected many cultural relics.

180
00:12:24,740 --> 00:12:25,900
We dared not go down,

181
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:28,060
but he wouldn't listen.

182
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,740
He went down alone.

183
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:32,820
I don't know what happened inside.

184
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:35,700
He seemed crazy

185
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,100
after he came up.

186
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:56,180
Dad...

187
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:58,420
Dad?

188
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:01,540
Uncle?

189
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:03,420
What's wrong with you?

190
00:13:05,300 --> 00:13:06,180
Oh no!

191
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:07,540
He was possessed.

192
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:09,300
Hurry up! Get the black dog's blood.

193
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:14,820
How dare you!

194
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:18,020
You were possessed.

195
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:23,020
Sorry, uncle.

196
00:13:23,020 --> 00:13:23,900
Uncle.

197
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:25,570
What's wrong with you, Jiahei?

198
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:34,900
Immortal Arts!

199
00:13:38,180 --> 00:13:39,460
You brat!

200
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:46,980
I'm not angry today.

201
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:57,620
How many tortoise shells did Zhou Jiahei get?

202
00:14:02,260 --> 00:14:03,180
One piece, I guess.

203
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:04,460
Are you sure?

204
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:08,540
Not really.

205
00:14:09,270 --> 00:14:10,700
It's been too long.

206
00:14:11,650 --> 00:14:12,940
Does he have more?

207
00:14:16,140 --> 00:14:17,020
Go on.

208
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:19,420
Later,

209
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:20,700
he went home

210
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:22,620
and locked himself in a room

211
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:24,500
for a whole three months.

212
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:25,820
He said he wanted

213
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,170
to decipher the Immortal Arts.

214
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:29,900
Back then,

215
00:14:30,220 --> 00:14:32,940
only his son Zhou Daye was with him.

216
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:34,780
Daye,

217
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:36,060
check this character.

218
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,260
Half a year later,

219
00:14:48,220 --> 00:14:49,100
he did...

220
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:52,220
actually

221
00:14:53,420 --> 00:14:55,020
killed a college girl

222
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,620
and dismembered her.

223
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:03,340
In our line of work,

224
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:05,270
it's usually clean and precise.

225
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:06,860
We avoid bloodshed.

226
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:07,740
But he...

227
00:15:11,990 --> 00:15:13,220
Wang Bingde said

228
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:14,820
he was possessed.

229
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:17,340
That tortoise shell he took

230
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:19,140
from the tomb might be cursed,

231
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:20,740
which is able

232
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:21,860
to cloud one's mind.

233
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:25,380
It details the method of immortality.

234
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:26,900
What's the method?

235
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:28,420
Sacrifice women,

236
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,580
and worship dark spirits.

237
00:15:32,060 --> 00:15:32,940
It's called

238
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:35,580
Immortality Ritual.

239
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:38,900
If it really worked,

240
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:41,580
why would the monarch lie in a tomb?

241
00:15:46,370 --> 00:15:47,380
Go on.

242
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:48,540
After they killed someone.

243
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,280
Soon after,

244
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:53,340
the police found them.

245
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:55,980
Wang Bingde suggested

246
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:57,620
offering a million

247
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,500
to bribe the detective captain.

248
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,460
But he

249
00:16:01,460 --> 00:16:02,340
firmly refused,

250
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:03,420
and wanted justice.

251
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:06,580
Afterwards...

252
00:16:07,980 --> 00:16:10,020
They captured the captain's daughter, right?

253
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:24,580
What does he say?

254
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:31,260
No compromise.

255
00:16:35,740 --> 00:16:36,780
So great!

256
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:39,020
So great!

257
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:40,620
Zhou Jiahei went mad.

258
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:43,490
After the captain refused him,

259
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,340
he knew it meant his end.

260
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,620
But,

261
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:50,260
before his time was up,

262
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:52,380
he wanted to teach the captain a lesson.

263
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:53,460
Dad,

264
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:54,420
let's leave together.

265
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:55,260
Exit from the south.

266
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:56,260
No one will find us.

267
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,740
I can't leave.

268
00:16:58,820 --> 00:16:59,700
You two go.

269
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:01,500
I'll handle this.

270
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:03,030
Only in this way will you both be safe.

271
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:05,580
Daye.

272
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:06,940
Dad.

273
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:09,340
Daye,

274
00:17:09,700 --> 00:17:10,580
live well.

275
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:13,100
I've taught you all I can.

276
00:17:14,020 --> 00:17:15,780
You must continue this path.

277
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:17,660
The immortality technique

278
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:20,700
is our family's legacy.

279
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:21,900
Remember that.

280
00:17:24,660 --> 00:17:25,540
Dad,

281
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:27,340
I remember.

282
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:32,020
- Xiang.
- Jiahei.

283
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:33,060
Promise me

284
00:17:33,060 --> 00:17:34,260
to look after Daye for me.

285
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:35,940
He's impulsive

286
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:37,500
and grew up without a mom.

287
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:39,940
When things happen,

288
00:17:41,020 --> 00:17:42,020
guide him often.

289
00:17:42,740 --> 00:17:43,620
Don't worry, Jiahei.

290
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:45,700
In the future, if I have food,

291
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:47,100
Daye won't go hungry.

292
00:17:47,740 --> 00:17:48,620
I'm relieved.

293
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:54,540
Leave here.

294
00:17:54,980 --> 00:17:55,860
Go.

295
00:17:56,940 --> 00:17:57,820
Come on!

296
00:17:58,700 --> 00:17:59,580
Just go!

297
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:08,140
Dad!

298
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,460
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

299
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:21,500
So great!

300
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:27,260
Being a great person comes at a cost.

