00:18:38,060 --> 00:18:38,940
So

302
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:41,460
he ended the girl himself,

303
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,180
and drew a cross

304
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:46,420
on her eyes.

305
00:18:52,620 --> 00:18:53,660
What's the meaning

306
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:55,100
of that mark?

307
00:18:57,060 --> 00:18:58,860
It's Zhou Jiahei's signature.

308
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:02,780
Since the day I met him,

309
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:05,020
he told me

310
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:07,740
not to look into his eyes.

311
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:15,340
Wang Bingde, the gang's underboss,

312
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:17,780
how did he evade

313
00:19:17,780 --> 00:19:18,660
the police back then?

314
00:19:19,580 --> 00:19:21,340
Not only is he meticulous in thought,

315
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:23,580
but he was also a sanda champion.

316
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:27,020
Zhou Jiahei knew

317
00:19:27,220 --> 00:19:28,300
trouble would come.

318
00:19:29,210 --> 00:19:31,020
So he kept Wang Bingde hidden,

319
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:32,960
just for entrusting his son

320
00:19:35,140 --> 00:19:36,060
to him in the future.

321
00:19:44,020 --> 00:19:45,140
What's wrong with your eye?

322
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,100
Haitao, you're here!

323
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:39,860
Master, these past months,

324
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:40,820
where have you been?

325
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:42,500
Couldn't find you.

326
00:20:42,740 --> 00:20:43,860
Just in the city,

327
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:44,740
laying low.

328
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,130
Haven't eaten, right? Get in.

329
00:20:47,220 --> 00:20:48,220
Let's grab a bite.

330
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:49,220
Not in a rush.

331
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:50,580
I came to ask you something.

332
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:55,140
Jiahei was gone.

333
00:20:56,020 --> 00:20:57,220
Now Daye is in charge.

334
00:20:58,740 --> 00:20:59,660
We are thinking

335
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:02,780
we will focus on business, no fieldwork.

336
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:04,780
Good.

337
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:07,180
But the former members

338
00:21:07,540 --> 00:21:08,660
are all gone.

339
00:21:09,820 --> 00:21:11,660
I was wondering if you

340
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:13,020
would like to come back

341
00:21:14,180 --> 00:21:16,180
and handle the fieldwork.

342
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:17,780
Your skills are impressive.

343
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:19,740
No one can match your skill

344
00:21:19,740 --> 00:21:20,940
in tomb blasting.

345
00:21:21,660 --> 00:21:22,540
Master,

346
00:21:23,820 --> 00:21:24,780
it's too risky.

347
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:26,580
I

348
00:21:26,980 --> 00:21:28,060
don't want to do it anymore.

349
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:29,940
From what you're saying,

350
00:21:30,900 --> 00:21:31,820
you look down on me?

351
00:21:31,820 --> 00:21:33,340
No, no, that's not it.

352
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:35,140
That's not what I mean.

353
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:36,220
- I really...
- Shut up.

354
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:38,260
What else can you do?

355
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:41,940
Always talking nonsense.

356
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:44,460
Apologize to Daye.

357
00:21:45,130 --> 00:21:46,220
Let's pretend we didn't hear

358
00:21:46,220 --> 00:21:47,420
what you just said.

359
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:51,700
Master, it's not nonsense.

360
00:21:51,940 --> 00:21:52,860
I

361
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:54,700
have a girlfriend now.

362
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,860
We are preparing to open a restaurant

363
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:58,860
in our hometown.

364
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:04,620
It seems like

365
00:22:04,620 --> 00:22:06,060
you had this planned all along,

366
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:07,370
ready to disband, right?

367
00:22:08,820 --> 00:22:09,700
Well,

368
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:12,460
it's a pity to waste your skills.

369
00:22:15,740 --> 00:22:16,620
I have no other way.

370
00:22:19,020 --> 00:22:20,140
Have you made up your mind?

371
00:22:32,420 --> 00:22:33,300
Alright.

372
00:22:33,780 --> 00:22:35,940
I can't force you.

373
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,460
I have my own business.

374
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:40,980
I can't stop you from yours, right?

375
00:22:42,620 --> 00:22:43,500
Master...

376
00:22:44,180 --> 00:22:46,940
You can run your small diner.

377
00:22:47,170 --> 00:22:48,190
When we need you here,

378
00:22:48,380 --> 00:22:49,500
you just blow up a tomb

379
00:22:50,020 --> 00:22:52,300
to earn extra money. Isn't that fine?

380
00:22:53,020 --> 00:22:53,900
Well,

381
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,260
hmm,

382
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:56,340
master,

383
00:22:57,700 --> 00:22:58,660
I want

384
00:22:59,180 --> 00:23:00,580
to quit completely.

385
00:23:02,140 --> 00:23:03,020
I'm done with it.

386
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:05,780
Are you sure?

387
00:23:08,980 --> 00:23:09,860
I'm sure.

388
00:23:11,140 --> 00:23:12,220
But you're different

389
00:23:12,220 --> 00:23:13,700
from the peripheral members.

390
00:23:14,900 --> 00:23:16,180
You know too much.

391
00:23:17,940 --> 00:23:19,380
Well, Daye,

392
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:20,260
master,

393
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:21,500
I won't say a word.

394
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:22,460
I'm tight-lipped.

395
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:23,380
You know that.

396
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:24,260
Really?

397
00:23:25,420 --> 00:23:26,300
Mr. Wang.

398
00:23:27,300 --> 00:23:28,180
Why not

399
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:29,620
follow the rules?

400
00:23:30,140 --> 00:23:31,700
Just bury him in a tomb.

401
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:34,380
- Daye, Daye.
- Master, please don't.

402
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:35,820
Haitao's been with us for years.

403
00:23:36,020 --> 00:23:36,900
Show me some respect.

404
00:23:36,900 --> 00:23:39,060
Master, can you speak for me?

405
00:23:39,060 --> 00:23:39,940
Haitao,

406
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:41,260
you're my apprentice.

407
00:23:41,660 --> 00:23:43,460
I really can't bear it.

408
00:23:43,660 --> 00:23:45,180
But there are rules.

409
00:23:45,780 --> 00:23:46,980
Or the team won't be obedient.

410
00:23:47,090 --> 00:23:47,940
Master...

411
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:48,940
Just one eye.

412
00:23:48,940 --> 00:23:50,700
No, Master, please.

413
00:23:50,700 --> 00:23:52,300
Daye, Daye.

414
00:23:52,300 --> 00:23:53,700
Guys, please don't.

415
00:23:53,700 --> 00:23:54,660
Please.

416
00:23:54,660 --> 00:23:55,780
I won't say a word. Trust me.

417
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:01,500
Losing one of your eyes

418
00:24:02,980 --> 00:24:04,470
is better than being buried.

419
00:24:13,460 --> 00:24:14,340
In this world,

420
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,820
what goes around comes around.

421
00:24:21,060 --> 00:24:22,780
These people have no limits.

422
00:24:24,500 --> 00:24:25,860
I'm really scared.

423
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:36,690
Did Wang Bingde ever mention

424
00:24:37,060 --> 00:24:38,200
how many people

425
00:24:39,380 --> 00:24:40,640
the Immortality Ritual requires?

426
00:24:46,170 --> 00:24:47,100
Seems he did mention it.

427
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:49,540
At least five

428
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:52,460
once.

429
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:55,260
It must be done in 100 days.

430
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:57,950
Complete the foundation

431
00:24:59,460 --> 00:25:00,340
within 100 days.

432
00:25:02,660 --> 00:25:03,540
Kill five people

433
00:25:04,740 --> 00:25:05,620
once?

434
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:08,860
Right.

435
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:10,660
If once isn't enough,

436
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:13,820
it has to be done several times.

437
00:26:23,260 --> 00:26:27,100
(Tripod, one piece)

438
00:26:28,380 --> 00:26:29,260
What's wrong, Senior?

439
00:26:30,540 --> 00:26:31,580
This tripod...

440
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:34,780
Let me study it.

441
00:26:35,940 --> 00:26:37,500
You've been studying it for a while.

442
00:26:39,540 --> 00:26:40,580
Focus on your own stuff.

443
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:41,610
Why do you care what I do?

444
00:26:43,060 --> 00:26:43,980
Alright, alright.

445
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:57,260
(Weight (kg) 4.8)

446
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:03,900
(Weight 4.0kg)

447
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:09,740
Don't you find this tripod

448
00:27:10,540 --> 00:27:11,420
a bit odd?

449
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:12,980
I don't find it odd.

450
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:14,470
I think you're a bit odd.

451
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:17,460
So,

452
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:19,500
you are very likely to not graduate.

453
00:27:21,780 --> 00:27:24,340
I'll just work here forever.

454
00:27:59,700 --> 00:28:00,620
Kong,

455
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:01,500
look here.

456
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:07,660
Look here.

457
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:13,500
(Fang Qi)

458
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:16,860
Fang Qi.

459
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:18,980
Is it fake?

460
00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:01,300
Excuse me. Is Fang Qi here?

461
00:29:01,870 --> 00:29:03,040
He's in the kiln over there.

462
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:04,060
Thanks.

463
00:29:23,060 --> 00:29:23,940
Fang Qi.

464
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,540
You are...?

465
00:29:28,580 --> 00:29:29,460
I'm Chen Nan.

466
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:31,500
Last year, my friend took me

467
00:29:31,500 --> 00:29:33,020
to have some bronze mirrors made here.

468
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:33,900
Do you remember?

469
00:29:35,300 --> 00:29:36,180
I have a vague memory.

470
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:38,540
Here's the thing.

471
00:29:38,540 --> 00:29:39,540
I have an item here.

472
00:29:39,540 --> 00:29:40,850
Could you take a look?

473
00:29:41,140 --> 00:29:42,060
Please, come inside.

474
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:42,940
Sure.

475
00:29:47,340 --> 00:29:48,300
Please have a look.

476
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:49,460
This tripod

477
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:50,740
was a gift from a friend.

478
00:29:50,740 --> 00:29:52,020
Is it your work?

479
00:29:58,380 --> 00:29:59,900
Yes, it's mine.

480
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:01,660
No doubt, my mark's here.

481
00:30:04,220 --> 00:30:05,060
Is this made

482
00:30:05,060 --> 00:30:07,340
from the same material as the real one?

483
00:30:07,620 --> 00:30:08,500
Pretty much.

484
00:30:08,700 --> 00:30:10,900
The same material ratio,

485
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:11,780
six to one ratio.

486
00:30:13,810 --> 00:30:14,930
How about the size?

487
00:30:15,220 --> 00:30:16,100
Also the same.

488
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:19,920
But the real one is one jin lighter.

489
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:21,020
Haven't you weighed it?

490
00:30:21,460 --> 00:30:22,940
I make crafts,

491
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:24,500
not selling meat.

492
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:29,420
Why do you think

493
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,540
the real one's lighter?

494
00:30:32,140 --> 00:30:33,220
Lighter?

495
00:30:34,380 --> 00:30:36,020
It shouldn't be, right?

496
00:30:37,900 --> 00:30:38,780
Unless

497
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:39,660
this tripod

498
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:41,580
has a compartment.

499
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:43,700
Ancient tripods often have

500
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:45,020
compartments.

501
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:46,700
Now some high-quality replicas

502
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,080
is also made with a compartment.

503
00:30:48,900 --> 00:30:50,160
Are you sure it's a compartment?

504
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:52,900
Well, if you have the real one,

505
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:54,120
just use medical imaging on it,

506
00:30:54,260 --> 00:30:55,140
and you'll know.

507
00:30:55,940 --> 00:30:56,940
But,

508
00:30:56,940 --> 00:30:58,500
why would it have a compartment?

509
00:30:59,460 --> 00:31:01,590
In the past, some had air pockets

510
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,430
left during casting,

511
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:05,300
and some contained

512
00:31:05,300 --> 00:31:06,540
metal objects

513
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:08,500
just to add weight,

514
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:09,960
making it feel substantial.

515
00:31:12,020 --> 00:31:14,500
But the real one is lighter than this.

516
00:31:15,120 --> 00:31:17,460
Do you think there's any other reason?

517
00:31:19,880 --> 00:31:21,580
I really don't know.

518
00:31:24,500 --> 00:31:25,380
You have to admit

519
00:31:25,380 --> 00:31:27,500
this tripod is really well-made.

520
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:28,900
Chen Nan,

521
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:30,460
I have one even better than this.

522
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:31,420
Let me show it to you.

523
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:02,100
Mom, I might not make it home this week.

524
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:04,220
No need to keep going back and forth.

525
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:05,460
It's alright.

526
00:32:05,860 --> 00:32:07,400
Take care of yourself, okay?

527
00:32:07,940 --> 00:32:09,030
Don't just eat cup noodles.

528
00:32:09,980 --> 00:32:11,380
Have something nutritious.

529
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:15,220
It's been a while since I had
instant noodles.

530
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:17,340
Don't worry, I'm eating well.

531
00:32:17,860 --> 00:32:19,460
You're not getting any younger.

532
00:32:20,340 --> 00:32:21,980
Time to find a girlfriend.

533
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:24,360
You should settle down.

534
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:26,100
Your dad and I

535
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:29,300
want a grandkid soon.

536
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:31,100
You,

537
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:33,060
please don't mention that man.

538
00:32:33,500 --> 00:32:34,620
He's your dad.

539
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:36,900
He cares about you.

540
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:39,380
I know that well.

541
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:42,380
He takes care of the family less.

542
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:45,300
Isn't it because he's busy with work?

543
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,820
When he's busy, he neglects home.

544
00:32:48,780 --> 00:32:49,740
But son,

545
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:51,780
he does love you.

546
00:32:52,870 --> 00:32:54,630
You should understand now.

547
00:32:55,220 --> 00:32:57,540
Those dedicated to police work

548
00:32:58,180 --> 00:33:01,220
rarely have time for family.

549
00:33:01,700 --> 00:33:02,580
Make time

550
00:33:03,260 --> 00:33:04,380
to visit your dad.

551
00:33:06,780 --> 00:33:07,660
Alright,

552
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:09,260
I won't keep you.

553
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:11,300
I'll come back when I can.

554
00:33:13,710 --> 00:33:14,580
Mom, you...

555
00:33:30,570 --> 00:33:31,960
Xiaoxing, I've been looking for you.

556
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:41,500
So, how's it going?

557
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:44,780
Wang Bingde left at midnight,

558
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:45,880
so there were no witnesses.

559
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:47,940
And there are no cameras in that village.

560
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:50,020
But Dafei just mentioned

561
00:33:50,130 --> 00:33:51,220
a villager lost a motorcycle

562
00:33:51,220 --> 00:33:52,220
yesterday.

563
00:33:52,940 --> 00:33:53,780
Yes.

564
00:33:53,780 --> 00:33:55,060
While investigating,

565
00:33:55,060 --> 00:33:56,300
we overheard villagers chatting.

566
00:33:56,780 --> 00:33:58,020
We found the motorcycle's owner.

567
00:33:58,320 --> 00:33:59,570
The time the motorcycle was lost

568
00:33:59,570 --> 00:34:00,820
coincides with the time

569
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:01,780
Wang Bingde disappeared.

570
00:34:01,780 --> 00:34:02,820
During our investigation,

571
00:34:03,370 --> 00:34:05,140
the gas station camera

572
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:06,940
captured the motorcycle passing.

573
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:09,100
But the rider wore a helmet,

574
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:10,210
so we couldn't see the face.

575
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:11,660
Judging by the build,

576
00:34:11,660 --> 00:34:12,640
it resembles Wang Bingde.

577
00:34:12,910 --> 00:34:14,780
And from the direction he went,

578
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:17,100
he likely headed to Baoyang City.

579
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:20,380
Immediately notify the local police

580
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:22,180
to ensure the wanted notice is sent

581
00:34:23,180 --> 00:34:24,570
to every driver, supermarket, hotel,

582
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,150
especially entertainment venues.

583
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,660
Wang Bingde won't stay idle.

584
00:34:27,860 --> 00:34:28,900
He might hunt again soon.

585
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:30,700
Got it.

586
00:34:32,300 --> 00:34:33,290
Zheng, send me the video.

587
00:34:33,290 --> 00:34:34,260
Quickly.

588
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:35,780
Captain, almost done.

589
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:40,790
All set, Captain Xu.

590
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:47,660
(Refueling Area-4,
Qunyi Station, Daliang Village)

591
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:48,980
Is this him?

592
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:49,860
Yes.

593
00:34:50,210 --> 00:34:51,140
The one with the helmet.

594
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,500
How's Lin doing?

595
00:34:55,700 --> 00:34:56,980
